  Student should have a familiar understanding, but may still have questions â­ â­ <br />
  Student should know of the concept, but need further resources to implement â­</p>

<ul>
  <li>Expose an API â­ â­ â­</li>
  <li>Use serializers to format JSON responses â­ â­ â­</li>
  <li>Test API exposure â­ â­ â­</li>
  <li>Compose advanced ActiveRecord queries to analyze information stored in SQL databases â­ â­</li>
  <li>Write basic SQL statements without the assistance of an ORM â­</li>
</ul>

<p><em>Note: See <a href="../../misc/learning_goals">Learning Goals</a> to see at what level these skills need to be by the final.</em></p>

